```plantuml
@startuml victor369basu_Real-time-stock-market-prediction

actor User
participant "producer.js" as Producer
participant Kafka
participant "consumer.js" as Consumer
participant "ml_consumer.js" as MLConsumer
participant "tf_model.js" as TFModel
participant "pre_process.js" as PreProcessor
participant "InstantiateDB.js" as MongoDB
participant "tf_train.js" as TFTrain
participant "tf_validate.js" as TFValidate
participant "server.js" as Server

User -> Server: Request model training
Server -> TFTrain: Start training
TFTrain -> MongoDB: Fetch historical data
MongoDB --> TFTrain: Return historical data
TFTrain -> PreProcessor: Preprocess data
PreProcessor --> TFTrain: Return scaled data
TFTrain -> TFModel: Train model
TFModel --> TFTrain: Return trained model
TFTrain -> MongoDB: Save model weights
TFTrain -> TFValidate: Validate model
TFValidate -> TFModel: Load model
TFModel --> TFValidate: Return model
TFValidate -> MongoDB: Fetch test data
MongoDB --> TFValidate: Return test data
TFValidate -> PreProcessor: Preprocess test data
PreProcessor --> TFValidate: Return scaled data
TFValidate -> TFModel: Validate model
TFModel --> TFValidate: Return metrics
TFValidate -> MongoDB: Save validation metrics
TFValidate --> Server: Return validation results
Server --> User: Display results

User -> Producer: Start data streaming
Producer -> Kafka: Publish stock data
Kafka -> Consumer: New stock data
Consumer -> MongoDB: Store raw data
Kafka -> MLConsumer: New stock data
MLConsumer -> PreProcessor: Preprocess data
PreProcessor --> MLConsumer: Return scaled data
MLConsumer -> TFModel: Load model
TFModel --> MLConsumer: Return model
MLConsumer -> TFModel: Predict
TFModel --> MLConsumer: Return prediction
MLConsumer -> MongoDB: Store prediction
MLConsumer -> Server: Push prediction update
Server -> User: Display real-time prediction

@enduml
```